      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Eighth grade examinations will\nbe held in the district schools Of\nSpokane county January 81 and %\nby local examiners to be appointed\nby County Superintendent McFar-\nland. All pupils desiring to take\nthe examination must have COM\npleted the eighth grade course in\nthe particular subjects for which\nthey desire to take the examina-\nton.\n\n\nThe questions to be asked are\nnot to be opened by the examiners\nuntil the morning of the examina-\nton, when the envelopes contain\ning the lists are to be opened in the\npresence of the pupils. This is\ndone to insure confidence of the\npupils in the fairness of the exam\nnation."
    }
  ]
